original_title: On the Couch, Volume Two: Toronto
overview: Renowned artist Tom Bianchi allows film makers Leach and Santry into his San Francisco studio and to accompany him on the road to Toronto, to reveal the intimate and very interactive relationship he has with his models as he creates his homo erotic imagery!
tagline: Photographer, Tom Bianchi visits Toronto to shoot a series of photographs using regular guys who had never modeled before.
title: On the Couch, Volume Two: Toronto
